  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    id="FAQ"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'What is PredictStream?',
        description:
          'PredictStream is an open-source platform that transforms raw, real-time event streams (e.g., IoT sensors, transaction logs, user interactions) into actionable AI-driven insights and automated responses. It leverages modular AI agents to clean, enrich, predict, and act on events as they happen.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How is PredictStream different from traditional data pipelines?',
        description:
          "Unlike batch-processing systems, PredictStream: <ul><li><strong>Operates in real time</strong>, closing the loop from insight â†’ action. </li><li><strong>Uses AI agents</strong> to handle messy, unstructured data (e.g., imputing missing values, inferring context).</li><li><strong>Supports self-improvement</strong> through feedback loops and operational telemetry.</li></ul>",
      },
      {
        title: 'What industries can benefit from PredictStream?',
        description:
          "Any domain with event-driven workflows! Examples: <ul><li><strong>IT/DevOps:</strong> Auto-remediate system failures.</li><li><strong>E-Commerce:</strong> Real-time cart abandonment fixes.</li><li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Automated patient reminders and scheduling.</li><li><strong>Industrial IoT:</strong> Proactive maintenance triggers.</li><li><strong>Financial Services:</strong> Freeze suspicious transactions in real time.</li><li>And many many more!</li></ul>",
      },
      {
        title: 'Do I need labeled data or predefined schemas to use PredictStream?',
        description:
          'No! PredictStreamâ€™s <strong>zero-knowledge learning agents</strong> can infer structure and semantics from raw streams, making it ideal for unlabeled or heterogeneous data. Custom agents can also integrate existing rules.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How does PredictStream ensure transparency and auditability?',
        description:
          "Every agent emits structured feedback, and all actions are logged as event streams themselves. This enables: <ul><li><strong>Real-Time monitoring:</strong> via dashboards.</li><li><strong>Auditability:</strong> Comprehensive logs for insights.</li><li><strong>Human-in-the-loop</strong> overrides where needed.</li></ul>",
      },
      {
        title: 'Is PredictStream scalable for high-velocity global data streams?',
        description:
          "Yes, but with caveats. The modular architecture supports horizontal scaling, and lightweight agents minimize latency. However, extreme-scale deployments (e.g., planetary IoT) may require custom optimizations - a focus of ongoing research.",
      },
      {
        title: 'When will PredictStream be available?',
        description:
          'We are currently in active development and expect to release an alpha version in Q3 2025. Early access will be available to select partners and community members before the public release. <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfXk5d0fGPTzuv9BA5cHOd7DBQDX8GmEDrhXzK6iI3-xnLWzg/viewform" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Join our community</a> to collaborate on development and share ideas.',
